            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName key="#Vir_magnificus" ref="#people/386"
                            >Perprand</persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_magnificus">virum magnificum</rs> filio bone memorie domni
                            <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/314">Walpert</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">duci</rs>
                        <foreign>vende</foreign> tibi domno <persName key="#Bishops"
                            ref="#people/320">Walprand</persName> gratias Deo <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopo</rs> parte mea de <rs key="#Salae #Demesnes">sala
                            sundriale</rs>, quam avire visum sum in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Salae #Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Acorns #Slave_labour #Slave"
                            ref="#places/749">Tocciano</placeName>, cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Cereals">terra</rs> et <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vinea</rs>, <rs key="#Acorns">silvis</rs>, vergaria, <rs key="#Oil"
                            >olivis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">pumis, arboribus</rs>; simol
                        et <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casas massaricia</rs> in ipso loco
                        Tocciano, cum territurii, vineis, silvis, vergarias, olivis, pumis,
                        arboribus, cum cultum et incultum, cum movile vel inmovile seo
                        semmoventibus, cum <rs key="#Slave_labour #Slave">serbus vel ancella</rs>,
                        quem avire visus sum in ipso loco, omnia et in omnebus mea portione in
                        integrus, excepto <persName key="#Slave_labour #Slave"><name
                                ref="Teofridulus">Teudifridulo</name></persName> cum muliere sua et
                        uno filius suum nomine <persName key="#Slave_labour #Slave"><name
                                ref="Personula">Personula</name></persName>, alii infantis sui.
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: auri soledos nomero tricenti. <foreign>Con la
                            clausola che se i beni </foreign>anplius adpretiata fueret super
                        tricenti soledos <foreign>Walprando </foreign><foreign>avrebbe pagato la
                            differenza; se al contrario sarebbe stata valutata meno, Perprando
                            avrebbe reso la differenza a Walprando. Pena in duplum.
                        Scrive</foreign>: <persName key="#Writer #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name
                                ref="Teudebertus">Teutpert</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viro devoto</rs>. (…) Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4">Luca</placeName>. <foreign>Sottoscrizioni:</foreign> +
                        Perprand viri magnifici venditori; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Sintrualdus"
                                >Suintroaldi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Ansualdus">Ansualdi</name></persName> testis; + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Fratellus"
                                >Fratelli</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio <persName><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alipert</name></persName> testis: + <persName
                            key="#Witness #Vir_devotus/vir_honestus"><name ref="Ermiteulus"
                                >Ermiteulo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Vir_devotus/vir_honestus">viri devoti</rs> filio quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Eriteus">Aritheo</name></persName> testis.
                            <foreign>Scrive:</foreign> Teupert.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                        <p>Muratori 1738-1742, V, 1011; MDL V/2, n. 44; CDL I, n. 105, pp. 301-303;
                    ChLA, XXXI, 935.</p>
                    </div>
